** {{ill|Kamo Akimasa|ja|賀茂在昌}} (1519/1520–1599)
* Adopted children:
** {{ill|Kadenokōji Akitane|ja|勘解由小路在種}} (son of {{ill|Kadenokōji Arikazu|ja|勘解由小路在康}})
** {{ill|Kadenokōji Akitaka|ja|勘解由小路在高}}

